headline: Westgate Super Site Receives CSX Select Site Platinum Designation
summary: JACKSONVILLE, Fla., Nov. 12, 2025 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- CSX (NASDAQ: CSX) today announced that the 365-acre Westgate Super Site in Dothan, Alabama, has been designated as a Platinum CSX Select Site. Select Sites are development-ready properties along the CSX network where standard land use considerations and comprehensive due diligence items have been previously addressed. These properties can meet the needs of a wide variety of manufacturers, significantly reducing the time required to construct
